00086 void Whirlpool::TruncatedFinal(byte *hash, size_t size)
00087 {
00088         ThrowIfInvalidTruncatedSize(size);
00089 
00090         PadLastBlock(32);
00091         CorrectEndianess(m_data, m_data, 32);
00092 
00093         m_data[m_data.size()-4] = 0;
00094         m_data[m_data.size()-3] = 0;
00095         m_data[m_data.size()-2] = GetBitCountHi();
00096         m_data[m_data.size()-1] = GetBitCountLo();
00097 
00098         Transform(m_state, m_data);
00099         CorrectEndianess(m_state, m_state, DigestSize());
00100         memcpy(hash, m_state, size);
00101 
00102         Restart();              // reinit for next use
00103 }
